high_descs: Turn right and walk toward the fridge, then turn left and move forward, and turn left again to face the white table.
Pick up the cabbage from the table.
Turn left and walk over to the sink.
Wash the cabbage in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the counter with the coffee machine.
Place the cabbage on the counter in front of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed cabbage on the counter by the coffee machine.

high_descs: Take a step right so you can walk past the stool and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left to walk to the table.
Pick up the head of lettuce that you see on the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink that's in front of you and to the right and stand facing it.
Wash the head of lettuce in the sink then get it back out and close the tap.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Put the head of lettuce on the counter to the right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean head of lettuce on the counter.

high_descs: Walk around the table to the other side
Take the cabbage on the table
Turn left, turn right, walk to the sink
put the cabbage in the sink, turn on the faucet, wash the cabbage, turn off the faucet, take the cabbage out
Turn left, walk to the counter by the stove
put the cabbage on the counter
anns.task_desc: wash the cabbage from the table, put in on the counter by the stove
